u\u00edn]] || align=center | 2014\u2013 || align=center | 200\n|}\n\n===Top 10 scorers===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Player !! Years !! {{tooltip|Goals|Goals scored}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Rubilio Castillo]] || align=center | 2014\u20132018 || align=center | 88\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[\u00c1ngel Obando]] || align=center | 1972\u20131986 || align=center | 77\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Amado Guevara]] || align=center | 1994\u20132000, 2007\u20132008, 2010\u20132013 || align=center | 72\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[\u00d3scar Rolando Hern\u00e1ndez|\u00d3scar Hern\u00e1ndez]] || align=center | 1968\u20131976 || align=center | 59\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Luis Alberto Reyes|Luis Reyes]] || align=center | 1976\u20131985 || align=center | 54\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Jairo Mart\u00ednez]] || align=center | 1997\u20132000, 2002\u20132005, 2006\u20132008 || align=center | 53\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Carlos Discua]] || align=center | 2011\u20132015, 2016\u20132018 || align=center | 52\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Mario Bland\u00f3n]] || align=center | 1969\u20131976 || align=center | 48\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Geovanny Castro]] || align=center | 1987\u20131988, 1990\u20131997 || align=center | 40\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Georgie Welcome]] || align=center | 2008\u20132013 || align=center | 39\n|}\n\n===List of Hat-tricks===\n[[Jairo Mart\u00ednez]] possesses the record of most [[hat-trick]]s for the club with a total of four.<ref>{{cite web |title=Bienvenido al club, Chino Discua... |url=https://www.elheraldo.hn/tag/737351-215/bienvenido-al-club-chino-discua |website=ElHeraldo.hn |publisher=[[La Prensa (Honduras)|El Heraldo]] |accessdate=12 August 2014}}</ref>  [[Denilson Costa]] remains as of today, the only player to score four goals in a single game for [[F.C. Motagua]] on 6 April 1997 against [[Independiente Villela]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Los futbolistas que anotaron tres o m\u00e1s goles en un mismo partido de la Liga Nacional de Honduras |url=https://www.diez.hn/liganacionaldehonduras/1263315-498/futbolistas-marcaron-goles-mismo-partido-liga-nacional-honduras |website=Diez.hn |publisher=[[La Prensa (Honduras)|Diario Diez]] |accessdate=28 February 2019}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Player<ref>{{cite web |title=\u00a1Conoce los jugadores que han anotado un Hat-Trick con la camisa de Motagua! |url=https://tiempo.hn/conoce-los-jugadores-que-han-anotado-un-hat-trick-con-la-camisa-de-motagua/ |website=Tiempo.hn |publisher=[[El Tiempo (Honduras)|El Tiempo]] |accessdate=25 February 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Moreira sexto extranjero con 'hat trick' en Motagua |url=https://www.diariomas.hn/2019/02/26/moreira-sexto-extranjero-con-hat-trick-en-motagua/ |website=DiarioMas.hn |publisher=[[La Tribuna (Honduras)|Diario Mas]] |accessdate=26 February 2019}}</ref> !! Date !! Rival\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Elio Banegas]] || 7 July 1966 || [[Platense F.C.|Platense]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Roberto Abrussezze]] || 9 July 1967 || [[C.D. Marath\u00f3n|Marath\u00f3n]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} Roberto Abrussezze || 18 August 1968 || [[C.D. Victoria|Victoria]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ado Baptista]] || 14 December 1969 || Victoria\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Pedro Caetano da Silva|Pedro da Silva]] || 6 September 1970 || [[C.D. Atl\u00e9tico Espa\u00f1ol|Atl\u00e9tico Espa\u00f1ol]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[\u00d3scar Rolando Hern\u00e1ndez|\u00d3scar Hern\u00e1ndez]] || 1972 || ''missing''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Mario Bland\u00f3n]] || 21 January 1973 || [[Broncos del Sur F.C.|Broncos]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Luis Alberto Reyes|Luis Reyes]] || 28 January 1979 || [[Real C.D. Espa\u00f1a|Real Espa\u00f1a]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CHI}} [[Mario Juvini]] || 1 June 1983 || Platense\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Leonel Suazo]] || ''missing'' || ''missing''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Geovanny Castro]] || 24 November 1991 || [[S\u00faper Estrella]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[C\u00e9sar Obando]] || 24 November 1991 || S\u00faper Estrella\n|-