onoce-los-jugadores-que-han-anotado-un-hat-trick-con-la-camisa-de-motagua/ |website=Tiempo.hn |publisher=[[El Tiempo (Honduras)|El Tiempo]] |accessdate=25 February 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Moreira sexto extranjero con 'hat trick' en Motagua |url=https://www.diariomas.hn/2019/02/26/moreira-sexto-extranjero-con-hat-trick-en-motagua/ |website=DiarioMas.hn |publisher=[[La Tribuna|Diario Mas]] |accessdate=26 February 2019}}</ref> !! Date !! Rival\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Elio Banegas]] || 7 July 1966 || [[Platense F.C.|Platense]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Roberto Abrussezze]] || 9 July 1967 || [[C.D. Marath\u00f3n|Marath\u00f3n]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} Roberto Abrussezze || 18 August 1968 || [[C.D. Victoria|Victoria]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ado Baptista]] || 14 December 1969 || Victoria\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Pedro Caetano da Silva|Pedro da Silva]] || 6 September 1970 || [[C.D. Atl\u00e9tico Espa\u00f1ol|Atl\u00e9tico Espa\u00f1ol]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[\u00d3scar Rolando Hern\u00e1ndez|\u00d3scar Hern\u00e1ndez]] || 1972 || ''missing''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Mario Bland\u00f3n]] || 21 January 1973 || [[Broncos del Sur F.C.|Broncos]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Luis Alberto Reyes|Luis Reyes]] || 28 January 1979 || [[Real C.D. Espa\u00f1a|Real Espa\u00f1a]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CHI}} [[Mario Juvini]] || 1 June 1983 || Platense\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Leonel Suazo]] || ''missing'' || ''missing''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Geovanny Castro]] || 24 November 1991 || [[S\u00faper Estrella]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[C\u00e9sar Obando]] || 24 November 1991 || S\u00faper Estrella\n|-\n| {{flagicon|URU}} [[\u00c1lvaro Izquierdo]] || 27 October 1992 || [[C.D.S. Vida|Vida]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[Presley Carson]] || 1993 || [[C.D. Petrotela|Petrotela]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} [[\u00c1lex \u00c1vila]] || ''missing'' || ''missing''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|HON}} Geovanny Castro || 8 December 1995 || Vida\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Denilson Costa]] ''(scored 4 goals)''